data.description:
FOUR garages, TWO full driveways and a CAR LIFT, along with a huge corner lot make this a dream home for a mechanic or car enthusiast. Unfinished poured concrete basement has enough space to hold all kinds of dismantled cars and parts, or finish into more living space. Enjoy space around you, like a house in the country, but with the nearby amenities of the city and quick access to interstate. Gleaming hardwoods in most of the home and loads of storage throughout. An updated kitchen has stainless steel appliances, an abundance of cabinets with roll-out shelves and newer laminate flooring. The Pella windows and hearth room will keep you warm. Spoil yourself in the
Spa-like, updated main bathroom, featuring heated floors and walk-in shower with ceramic tiles walls and built-in
seat plus solid wood vanity, linen cabinet, and pull-out cabinet for the main floor laundry area! Well-maintained systems include regular maintenance, high efficiency furnace, newer water heater, copper plumbing throughout, and water filtration system.  Step into the great outdoors to a huge yard with a large Pergola and 3 raised garden beds. And then...for that avid car-lover, there’s the two basements, one with two levels. PLUS FOUR garages! Multi-level basement is poured concrete & Steel I-Beams. Storage area, floor drain. 24 square-foot bay, 8,000 lb Hydraulic Atlas car lift and Lots of working space. The front of the home has beautiful, mature trees. Plenty of room for parking with the main drive in front featuring a turn around. The second drive extends from the street, down to the second set of garages and includes sensor lights. The 9.5 x 9 garage doors open individually, and the 11-foot ceiling is covered in LED shop lights and fluorescents. The great outdoor space can be accessed from the kitchen sliding door, or from the basement door. The Pergola has its own lighting and is approximately 16 x 16. The property extends back to the treeline.
